{"tid":1821370,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"ptsd點上前線？","createTime":"2020-01-12T08:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T20:19:06.000Z","uid":177082,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e6aaadc9dc6a63b93d288e5d28d1973efcade43b","tid":1821370,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:34:47.000Z","msg":"發夢有個朋友<br />\n佢本身已經有情緒問題（抑鬱焦慮）聽到巨響會Panic Attack 例如有人突然無啦啦大聲鬧人佢已經會心跳加快呼吸困難<br />\n雖然催淚彈嗰啲都好大聲 但係佢都係忍住咗 上咗幾次前線 遮陣 滅煙 <br />\n<br />\n之後開始抑鬱越黎越嚴重 再加啲ptsd症狀 開始迴避香港有關嘅資訊<br />\n<br />\n佢有繼續做和理非遊行 但係無動力再上返前線<br />\n佢覺得自己好無用<br />\n佢覺得自己反正每日都好想死 點解唔上返前 反正都係死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以點幫佢 大家係度同佢講幾句吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db38687ea8fa89babfa837a968e827d843c41de","tid":1821370,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:36:56.000Z","msg":"好辛苦 好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25cc93fbe962d61b28d0ff866cb9f6978b85c941","tid":1821370,"uid":13395,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啦"},{"pid":"0ebafec526c79ec5d04f3096747887cde51363a7","tid":1821370,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25cc93fbe962d61b28d0ff866cb9f6978b85c941","tid":1821370,"uid":13395,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T08:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快啦"},"citedBy":